{"tid":1692720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門街坊長遮鎖門死守商場","createTime":"2019-11-04T08:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:25:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8b86495fb86f8c4ed68e19100dd91e747bb51f","tid":1692720,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/RSUDDPWKDHUU2SLMWYU4CJVU2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FRSUDDPWKDHUU2SLMWYU4CJVU2A%2F&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=160c7c91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191104%2FRSUDDPWKDHUU2SLMWYU4CJVU2A%2F&h=a29030f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191104/RSUDDPWKDHUU2SLMWYU4CJVU2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n屯門街坊長遮鎖門死守商場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/-xf0DACEIS6e-j6zoBHZiLZcHCY=/802x552/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/RK6TY3OVUAJCTTNLU27F7OVUAQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F-xf0DACEIS6e-j6zoBHZiLZcHCY%3D%2F802x552%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FRK6TY3OVUAJCTTNLU27F7OVUAQ.gif&h=ab7e3b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門時代廣場內市民用長傘及索帶鎖上商場玻璃門，令警察無法進入。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】市民昨七區行街反警暴但警方變本加厲，硬闖多區商場搜捕示威者，屯門區倖免於難，防暴警嘗試闖入屯門時代廣場，但市民用長傘及索帶鎖上商場玻璃門，令警察無法進入。至傍晚商場提早關門，商舖紛紛落閘暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：立場記者被扣手銬拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防暴警向平台人群擎槍<br />\n<br />\n昨下午3時半，大批市民在屯門時代廣場一帶聚集，響應行街反警暴活動，其間有示威者從平台向下面的防暴警員投擲雞蛋及木梯等雜物，防暴警一度向平台的人群擎槍示警，之後嘗試進入商場進行搜捕，但市民在屯門時代廣場連接大會堂平台的主要出入口，用長傘攔在玻璃門的手柄上，又用索帶綁起玻璃門手柄，結果令警察無法進入。<br />\n<br />\n警民衝突期間，時代廣場及屯門市廣場多間商舖及食肆先後拉閘關門，當中包括多次被「裝修」的吉野家及優品360。至下午5時許，屯門時代廣場宣佈提早關閉，商舖相繼落閘，保安員陸續鎖上出入口玻璃門並貼出關門告示，商場於傍晚6時關閉。警方其後發新聞稿，譴責示威者堵塞商場主要出入口等行為是極不負責任，又指一旦商場發生緊急事故，將嚴重阻礙市民離開。<br />\n<br />\n■記者邵靖妍"},{"pid":"b3c3387598c9dd67f871cba7d7f65406d769af21","tid":1692720,"uid":103325,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"警方其後發新聞稿，譴責示威者堵塞商場主要出入口等行為是極不負責任，又指一旦商場發生緊急事故，將嚴重阻礙市民離開。<br />\n<br />\n咁而家有無緊急事故發生？無呀嘛，因為好彩有市民阻止佢地進入至無事發生咋"},{"pid":"f617ca6021cce4e226ca3dd47d01cbf50c452313","tid":1692720,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"諗起Dead rising 依隻game <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679cfaf9afd99456d9b1dd8790873cfa627a022b","tid":1692720,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"有班唔受控嘅癫狗想沖入黎咬你,係咪要係大脾灑埋鹽胡椒等佢地黎咬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591263b801ce4e9ecb97dd789e4e7c6fbf528fd1","tid":1692720,"uid":11540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"679cfaf9afd99456d9b1dd8790873cfa627a022b","tid":1692720,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"有班唔受控嘅癫狗想沖入黎咬你,係咪要係大脾灑埋鹽胡椒等佢地黎咬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母殘體字"},{"pid":"5665ec4e12bfc1feb3c045e5dc4cfc0381c1304e","tid":1692720,"uid":145558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"你班撚樣唔入黎咪無緊急事故囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acc8f3d479dca03ef5abe5a08dcf0235ec42a9c","tid":1692720,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"爆門呀警蛆 又唔係未試過爆閘"},{"pid":"bc2848da0a424863aef26a798ecfd015cc40dfab","tid":1692720,"uid":124473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"今次真係好彩<br />\n其實有好多位佢地可以入到黎......"},{"pid":"79bc6b7463916f9b7fdf6c57d5c9d8fc34007e85","tid":1692720,"uid":973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1